---
title: Smart Pork Satay Salad with Marinated Radishes and Mango
description: South Asian-inspired flavours take centre stage in this yummy salad. Ground pork is sautéed with aromatic ginger, then dressed in a nutty vinaigrette. Juicy bursts of pickled radish and mango bring bold bites of freshness.
